<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>License Reset Portal - Envauth</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-8">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 max-w-2xl w-full">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">License Reset Portal</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Use this service to unlock your license code for purchased products and reuse it on a new machine or IP address, depending on your product type.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How it works:</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li><strong>Machine ID binding:</strong> For apps and tools, licenses are bound to a unique machine ID. Reset to activate on a different machine.</li>
                <li><strong>IP address binding:</strong> For server-side PHP scripts, licenses are bound to an IP address. Reset to activate on a different server.</li>
                <li><strong>Secure authentication:</strong> Log in with your Envato account to reset your license.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4 mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What you'll need:</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li>✓ Your license code</li>
                <li>✓ Your Envato account credentials</li>
                <li>✓ A reason for resetting (optional)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/license/reset" class="inline-block bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                Continue to License Reset
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
